00:02:29.720 --> 00:02:35.680
[Amit Varma]: a show called The Scene and the Unseen, because B.P. Medan really is one of those unseen heroes

00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:42.120
[Amit Varma]: whose contribution to our history is outsized. Well, unseen no more. Narayani's book is available

